					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2018455598cf1d56007c5d06ce7b2901?s=74&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2018455598cf1d56007c5d06ce7b2901?s=148&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-74 photo' height='74' width='74' />						<b class="fn">Francisco Ribeiro</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://www.lightbluetouchpaper.org/2020/04/12/contact-tracing-in-the-real-world/#comment-1945858">
							<time datetime="2020-04-13T00:14:09+00:00">
								2020-04-13 at 00:14 UTC							</time>
