						</a>
											</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Contact tracing is dead. It&#8217;s over. It&#8217;s too late. The horse is out of the barn and running down the road. Everyone is already exposed. There is no point to tracing contacts for millions or billions of people. It&#8217;s absurd. Find another problem to solve.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

