				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>No-one thinks a vaccine should be deployed generally without clinical trials first. We are in a position with contact tracing apps that not only have they not been trialled, we don&#8217;t even have a trial methodology to evaluate their medical AND social consequences.</p>
<p>By all means develop them so they might provide proteection from future outbreaks, but deploying them fullscale now will leave us open to unforseen consequences</p>
