						</a>
											</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Here is an <a href="https://www.brookings.edu/techstream/inaccurate-and-insecure-why-contact-tracing-apps-could-be-a-disaster/" rel="nofollow ugc">excellent piece</a> by Ashkan Soltani, Ryan Calo and Carl Bergstrom which says many of the things my post did, but more eloquently and completely.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

